description:
Ichigo is an honor student of the Mistilteinn academy seen as a natural-born leader. She is childhood friends with http://anidb.net/ch92216 [Hiro] and cares about his well being, despite her cool demeanor. Her Franxx partner is http://anidb.net/ch92213 [Gorou].
Source: Darling in the Franxx Wiki
name: Ichigo
